  "cost_gp": 400.0,
  "description": "Wondrous Item, Uncommon\n\nWhile holding this fan, you can cast Gust of Wind (save DC 13) from it. Each subsequent time the fan is used before the next dawn, it has a cumulative 20 percent chance of not working; if the fan fails to work, it tears into useless, nonmagical tatters.\n\nRoll for Chance of Not Working: [[/r 1d5cs&gt;@item.uses.spent]]\n\nFoundry Note\n\nEach of use of Gust of Wind expends a use of this item and is reset at dawn. The inline roll above rolls 1d5 and checks if the value is higher than the number of uses to handle the cumulative 20 percent chance of not working. It will return \"1\" if it's successful and \"0\" if it fails.",
